Happy birthday!

JetBlue Airways flight 1121 service from Detroit Metro Int'l Airport (KDTW) to Washington Reagan (KDCA) in the Airbus A320. We depart into an ongoing birthday celebration for the approach controller and arrive into DCA on the runway 19 River Visual approach. Artificial intelligence tries to steal my cabin announcements.
